{
  "stem": "2581.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But during-- during that time, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] my-- my mind was completely so absorbed about the-- the tragedy that has happened step after step.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Here we lost the mother and the brother, now I'm concerned about where is my father?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What is going to happen to him?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He's getting older, he's had all these-- these cysts on his-- on his neck and he wasn't getting better.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And here I saw they were sending people-- this much we understood.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When we saw that they were taking only healthy people one way, we knew that the others are not going to a good place, but we didn't know exactly what.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, we heard the rumors that no one would believe, but there wasn't talk yet.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "At that time, I didn't hear anything about-- about chimneys, you know?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We heard about it and saw it later, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So now you're in there and you've got the uniform on, and then what happened?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They just made us take little stones from here and put them there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They kept us busy for-- for at least eight days.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they-- if you didn't move fast enough, they would beat you.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And mostly that would beat us is the people in the striped-- in the striped suits, those kapos, those people that were the-- the hardened-- they were criminals.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Or-- or maybe some people just that wanted to survive.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They kept-- they kept beating us for the, you know, to show for the Germans that were watching them with the dogs that they are the-- working for them.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But these people must have thought that they will be the ones to survive.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, everyone thought they would be the one to survive.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
